        ],
        "content": [
            "王子一行人终于打倒了莱昂尼多。\\n然而，依旧不肯屈服的莱昂尼多\\n与王子发生了信念上的碰撞。\\n事情在沙音的努力下终于要告一段落之际，\\n法尔艾斯突然出现，向一行人发起攻击。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哈啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "呃啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "成功了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "还没完！别以为这点本事\\n就能阻止我的霸道！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "呐！这种感觉……\\n和福波斯他们一样！\\n难道……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "快住手！再这样下去你会\\n像那些福波斯一样燃尽的！\\n你到底知不知道啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "不用你说！站在安全的地方\\n当旁观者的人哪能称霸！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "立于顶点才是霸道！\\n身先士卒才是霸道！\\n我走过的地方才能称作道！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "统帅他人者，就要以身犯险！\\n只有这样，后面的人才会跟上来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "开山、伐林、填河。\\n想开辟理想的道路，就要牺牲一切！\\n哪怕是自己的身躯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呃……呜、呜呜……\\n住手吧，哥哥！\\n呃！既然如此……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你要用你那半吊子的龙化\\n跟我抗衡吗！太不自量力了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "为什么啊，哥哥！\\n为什么不惜牵连无辜的人！\\n连你自己也……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你真的屈服于魔神了吗！？\\n效忠狄涅尔帝国了吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "愚蠢。你什么都不懂！\\n你知道什么是魔神、什么是狄涅尔吗！？\\n你考虑过这些吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "这个世界需要\\n尽快摆脱龙的统治！\\n你为什么就是不懂！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "龙的统治？\\n龙不是世界的基石、\\n我们的友邻吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你会这么想，\\n是因为被灌输了这种想法……\\n我所说的统治，就是指这个！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "我要尽快解除这充满谎言的契约，\\n让这个世界重新\\n回到人类的掌控中！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "充满谎言的契约？\\n你在说什么……这是什么意思，\\n告诉我，莱昂尼多哥哥！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "告诉你这种\\n笃信人龙关系的家伙有什么用。\\n我的道路要由自己亲手开拓！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哥哥，为什么……\\n你为什么会如此焦虑！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "就算如你所说，\\n也没必要采取这种\\n会导致大量牺牲的办法啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你以为厌恶被龙统治的人\\n只有我一个吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你说什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "厌恶被龙统治、\\n想将这个世界据为己有的人，\\n除了我还有别人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "要是那些人推翻了龙的统治，\\n你觉得这个世界会变成什么样？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "在龙的统治下过着安稳日子的人\\n将无人能够幸免！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "那就需要我……身为人类的我\\n来把这个世界从龙的统治下\\n解放出来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "莱昂尼多哥哥……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "既然如此，\\n你就更不该和魔神联手！\\n为什么，你就是不愿相信人类呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "愚蠢！这个世界就是轻信他人的下场！\\n连这个道理都不懂的人\\n根本不值得我浪费口舌！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "消失吧！\\n炼金完爆！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210001_01",
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呜、呜哇啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呜……呃啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "……\\n你很碍事，尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "越多人从你小子那里看到希望，\\n就会让龙的统治变得越稳固。\\n所以我要在这里干掉你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "唔！？\\n呃啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哈啊、哈啊、哈啊……\\n我的身体……已经到极限了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "不过，只要再给你最后一击……\\n好了，做好觉悟吧……\\n尤蒂尔。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我不会……让你这么做！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "是沙音啊……你也被这家伙感化了吗。\\n你不知道给别人带来希望的行为\\n有多么愚蠢吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "这话不该你来说吧……\\n你可是建立起了巴尔加海姆啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "巴尔加海姆是一个弱肉强食的城市。\\n住在那里的所有人，\\n都想踩着别人向上爬。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "没错，希望要靠自己的双手去争取。\\n不能把希望寄托在别人身上。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "不。当时的我们是因为有了\\n爬上来的希望，才能战斗下去。\\n因为在称霸之路上前行的人在那里……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "对于那时的我们来说，\\n你就是希望啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "竟然说我是希望！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "你屈服于魔神，舍弃了自己的霸道！\\n不再靠自己的力量向上爬，\\n而是去求魔神给予你力量！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "可是尤蒂尔不一样。\\n他并没有去乞求，\\n而是靠自己的力量向上爬。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "他开辟的道路，才能称之为霸道！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哼，笑话！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "呃……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "输了……我……竟然输了吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "莱、莱昂尼多……哥哥……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "尤蒂尔……\\n我的命……就由你来取吧。\\n这是身为王者的义务。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "哥哥……我做不到。\\n你别再插手魔神的事，\\n回到巴尔加海姆去吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你害怕夺走兄长的性命吗？\\n真是个软弱的弟弟……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不管你怎么说，我都做不到。\\n赢的是我们，哥哥。\\n所以你得服从我们……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "你这家伙……\\n想留下我的命羞辱我吗！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你误会了。\\n哥哥从父王那里接到的任务，\\n应该是对抗北面的威胁。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_12_07_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
